data.description: Like new 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath townhome in the highly sought after community of Portico.  New carpet upstairs in the bedrooms, home is like new only 2 years old. Tile flooring downstairs, stainless appliances, quartz counter tops with 2 inch wood blinds. Private back yard with 6 ft privacy fence and open patio. Great location to I75 and shopping. There is a lot of community amenities to enjoy pickleball, tennis, basketball, swimming and much more. Close to the airport for quick travel. Call for your private showing.
